edu.ncsu.csc.itrust.beans

? PrescriptionReportBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc.itrust.beans.PrescriptionReportBean

  • public class PrescriptionReportBean
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the container bean for the Prescription Report requirement. It contains a PrescriptionBean (which in turn contains a Medication Bean), and an office visit bean.

    This was made so that the prescription report could be done all in one clean query.

    See PrescriptionBean See OfficeVisitBean

    Andy Meneely
